	<span>
		🛠️ Training Details
	</span>
</h2>
<p>The training is performed in two stages:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Pretraining</strong> on the <em>Targoman News</em> dataset  </li>
<li><strong>Fine-tuning</strong> on multiple synthetic datasets</li>
</ol>
