	</a>
	<span>
		Stage 1: Pretraining
	</span>
</h3>
<ul>
<li>We use an <strong>asymmetric</strong> setup.</li>
<li>Input formatting:<ul>
<li>Titles are prepended with <code>"سوال: "</code></li>
<li>Texts are prepended with <code>"متن: "</code></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Loss function: <code>CachedMultipleNegativesRankingLoss</code></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="relative group flex items-baseline">
	<a id="stage-2-fine-tuning" class="block pr-1.5 text-lg md:absolute md:p-1.5 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover:opacity-100 md:right-full" href="#stage-2-fine-tuning" rel="nofollow">
