	</a>
	<span>
		Stage 2: Fine-tuning
	</span>
</h3>
<ul>
<li>Loss functions:<ul>
<li><code>CachedMultipleNegativesRankingLoss</code></li>
<li><code>CoSENTLoss</code></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Used across multiple synthetic datasets</li>
</ul>
